                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/14592.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Garrett</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Nuevo Laredo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-03-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 14, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>General Ricaut informed me this morning that he will probably be forced to
                    evacuate this city before many days and asked me to request permission from the
                    Department to cross his wounded and take them by railroad through American
                    territory to Matamoros.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Garrett.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
